channel.title: Hey need help getting into dodian
channel.description: hey. i cant seem to get on to dodian, its saying to many connections from ur address. when i really only just opened and got no other connections.... i tryed restarting my computer, turning off my internet and reconecting. it wont work... after a while i left the server and went to enkrona. i went back after half an hour and it said invalid user name and password. so i make up a new account like im a new player, so i log in and get to around lvl 50, then it laags and logs me out. i try and log back in and it sais my account is already logged in... i try my other account and it says to many connections from your address... some one help me please [br][size=1]Posted on: April 21, 2007, 06:51:22 PM[/size][hr]some one help me please.
